text: Kyburg may refer to: *Kyburg, Zurich, a former municipality in the part of the municipality of Illnau-Effretikon in the Canton of Zurich, Switzerland *Kyburg Castle, a castle in the municipality Kyburg, Switzerland *The House of Kyburg that took their name from the castle *Kyburg County, a former administrative unit in the Canton of Zurich, Switzerland *Kyburg-Buchegg, a former municipality in the part of the municipality of Buchegg in the Canton of Solothurn, Switzerland
title: Kyburg
